<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Joyeux Anniversaire Mon Amour !</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.css" />
    <style>
        :root {
            --rouge: #ff0000;
            --jaune: #ffcc00;
            --vert: #22ad27;
            --violet: #8e44ad;
        }

        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100%;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #000;
        }

        .swiper {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .swiper-slide {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Pages avec tes couleurs vives */
        .page-oursons { background-color: var(--rouge); }
        .page-lettre  { background-color: var(--violet); }
        .page-gateau  { background-color: var(--jaune); color: #000; }
        .page-photos  { background-color: var(--vert); }

        h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 20px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: bold; }
        p { font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 500; }

        .gif-container img {
            width: 280px;
            border: 5px solid white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .gateau { font-size: 100px; animation: pulse 1.5s infinite; }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }

        /* Grille pour tes photos */
        .photo-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 350px;
        }

        .photo-item {
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            border: 4px solid white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #eee;
        }

        .photo-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .hint {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 40px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="swiper">
        <div class="swiper-wrapper">
            
            <div class="swiper-slide page-oursons">
                <h1>SURPRISE ! ❤️</h1>
                <div class="gif-container">
                    <img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/v1.Y2lkPTc5MGI3NjExM3ZleHh4emJreXp6ZzR6ZzR6ZzR6ZzR6ZzR6ZzR6ZzR6ZzR6ZzR6JmVwPXYxX2ludGVybmFsX2dpZl9ieV9pZCZjdD1n/vYGUfSZp5n9E4/giphy.gif" alt="Oursons qui s'embrassent">
                </div>
                <div class="hint">SWIPE POUR LA SUITE 👉</div>
            </div>

            <div class="swiper-slide page-lettre">
                <h1>MA LETTRE 💌</h1>
                <p>
                    Mon amour, en ce jour spécial, je voulais te dire à quel point tu comptes pour moi. 
                    Chaque moment à tes côtés est précieux. Je te souhaite le plus beau des anniversaires !
                    Je t'aime plus que tout. ❤️
                </p>
                <div class="hint">CONTINUE DE SWIPER...</div>
            </div>

            <div class="swiper-slide page-gateau">
                <h1>FAIS UN VŒU ! 🎂</h1>
                <div class="gateau">🎂</div>
                <p>Joyeux Anniversaire !<br>Souffle tes bougies !</p>
                <div class="hint">DERNIÈRE SURPRISE 👉</div>
            </div>

            <div class="swiper-slide page-photos">
                <h1>NOUS DEUX 📸</h1>
                <div class="photo-grid">
                    <div class="photo-item"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/4nsMwKcH/3a994eb7-c943-43d4-a51d-c5e00d3911f9.jpg"></div>
                    <div class="photo-item"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/Bjr7Ftsb/IMG-2653.jpg"></div>
                    <div class="photo-item"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/JGyQQmpc/IMG-2715.png"></div>
                    <div class="photo-item"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/MvGL2hdq/IMG-4726.jpg"></div>
                </div>
                <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">Pour toujours ensemble.</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        const swiper = new Swiper('.swiper', {
            loop: false,
            grabCursor: true,
            effect: 'slide'
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
